2 Level 4 monstersOnce per turn: You can detach 1 Xyz Material from this card, then target 1 "Gagaga" monster you control; this turn, that target can make a second attack during each Battle Phase. When another monster is targeted for an attack: You can change this card to Defense Position, then change the attack target to this card, and you proceed to damage calculation.
